  ('investigation-2b298e71-moex-00062', 'investigation-2b298e71', 'investigation-2b298e71-moex-113-de0a21a2', 'sub-investigation-2b298e71-01', NULL, 'essay', '甲、乙為朋友，乙在賣場銷售手錶，某日甲在乙工作時探望乙，且在兩人
